            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Page Numbers</td>
              <td>Top-right header or bottom-center footer</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3>Navigating Referencing Styles</h3>

        <p>Correct referencing protects you against academic 
        plagiarism. Always check your course handbook for the 
        specific referencing guidelines required.</p>

